Let me ask you

19
00:00:36.560 --> 00:00:36.999
What was Fù Jiā Háo’s purpose

20
00:00:37.760 --> 00:00:38.599
In having you pretend to be my parents to approach me?

21
00:00:39.960 --> 00:00:40.999
Son, you have to believe us

22
00:00:41.040 --> 00:00:43.159
We really are

23
00:00:43.560 --> 00:00:45.159
Your biological parents

24
00:00:45.160 --> 00:00:46.679
Yes, yes

25
00:00:46.680 --> 00:00:47.679
You won’t talk, huh?

26
00:00:48.320 --> 00:00:48.679
Don’t blame me for being ruthless

27
00:00:50.120 --> 00:00:50.799
I’ll talk, I’ll talk